settings.custom_html:
<style>
.container {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.left-column {
  flex: 0 0 25%;
  order: 1;
  padding: 15px;
}

.right-column {
  flex: 1;
  order: 2; 
  Padding: 15px;
}

.left-sub-nav ul{
	padding-left:15px;
}

.left-sub-nav ul li{
	padding:4px 5px 4px 0;
	list-style:none;
	font-size: 13px;
}

.clearer{
clear:both;
}

.left-sub-nav .nav-group{
	border: 1px solid #ccc;
	margin-bottom:10px;
}

.left-sub-nav .main-nav-cat{
	background-color:#303e49;
	padding:10px 10px;
	color:#fff;
}


/* Add media query to change the layout on smaller screens */

@media (max-width: 1000px) {
  .left-column {
	flex: 0 0 35%;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 767px) {
  .left-column {
	flex: 0 0 100%;
    order: 2; /* move the left column back to the first position */
  }
  .right-column {
	flex: 0 0 100%;
    order: 1; /* move the right column back to the second position */
  }
}

/* calculator styles */
.calc-main-column{
float:left;
width:69%;

}
.calc-main-table{
	float:right;
	width:30%;
}


.calc-main-column label{
	display:block;
	padding:5px;
}

.calc-main-column .input-text{
	font-size:18px;
	line-height:20px;
	padding:5px;
}


.calc-main-table .table{
border-spacing:0;
width:100%
}
.calc-main-table .table thead > tr > th{
background-color:#303e49;
color:#fff;
font-size:15px;
padding:5px;
}
.calc-main-table .table thead > tr > th
.calc-main-table .table tbody > tr > th, .table tfoot > tr > th,
.calc-main-table .table thead > tr > td, .table tbody > tr > td,
.calc-main-table .table tfoot > tr > td{
	border-top:1px solid #dddddd;
}
.table-striped > tbody > tr:nth-child(2n+1) > td,
.table-striped > tbody > tr:nth-child(2n+1) > th{
	background-color:#f9f9f9;
}

@media only screen and (max-width:550px){
	.calc-main-table{
		float:none;
		width:100%;
	}
	.calc-main-column{
	float:none;
	width:100%;

	}

}



</style>
